In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Nathaniel H. SPEIGHTS. No. D-3029. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 29, 2018.

Nathaniel H. Speights, of Washington, District of Columbia, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
